version_description: Added new languages Danish and Macedonian.
Function of QR code and Bar code generation added.

11 carriers added ->UK Mail，SailPost，LaserShip，Continents，HIS，Hyperlink，DBB，TZT，Tonda Global，TopEx，Asendia HK.
The registered e-mail address can be changed.
QR code and barcode generated can be saved.
iOS native return supported.

2. Add memos to the numbers immediately after adding the numbers.

Jingle bells! New features of 17TRACK this Christmas!
[New carriers]
12 carriers added:Caribou, QFL, 56JJY, YDGJ, YL, CKEEX, FN Logistics, JNJ, YYJ, CZRS, ZCE, Best Inc..
[New parcel information]
More information additive to your parcels: product names, order number, order time, etc.
[New deals]
A great number of coupons and featured products for your selection!
17TRACK, stays with you this Christmas!

[Optimization]
Optimized search function to help you find the tracking numbers or some hot deals...
[Minor bug fixes]
Fixed a minor issue for the notification function.
Fixed malfunction issue for iOS system when slide down to update.

【New feature issued - Email tracking service】
Forward your emails to us and we'll analyze/add tracking numbers to your account directly – We'll also deliver notifications & updates for these numbers that will help to improve your tracking experience.

【Optimization】
Optimized the red-dot prompt for the new updates, so you won't miss any important information.
Strengthened the security of the password to help you keep your account secure.
Fixed some minor bugs.
